Package ru.nsu.plodushcheva

Class ElGradeBook

  • java.lang.Object
    • ru.nsu.plodushcheva.ElGradeBook
  • public class ElGradeBook
extends java.lang.Object
    The student's electronic grade book, which stores the student's name, the result of his/her qualification work, current semester number, An array with semesters. Each semester is a HashMap with pairs. course name - information about the grades of the course.
